          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1662397183064-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and chop roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> and <strong>remaining pesto </strong>to the white sauce and cook for 1-2 min further or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>creamed spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1662397187584-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
